  "detailed_description": "Backrooms: Liminal Conflict is a PvP backrooms game with different factions.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >M.E.G. Researcher</h2>Play as the M.E.G. Researcher class, trapped in the depths of the backrooms. Your objective: escape to the safety of an M.E.G. outpost. Along the way, you'll find aid from M.E.G. Mercenaries, ready to support you. But beware the Followers of Jerry, a sinister cult lurking in the shadows, intent on indoctrinating all wanderers in backrooms.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2787750/extras/0b03b8a46ed234c03fd6184e70bdea11.avif?t=1737715437\" width=598 height=444 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >M.E.G. Mercenary</h2>Take on the role of a M.E.G. Mercenary with a single directive: find and protect the researchers at all costs. Nothing will stand in your way as you eliminate any threats blocking your path.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2787750/extras/8102ac290c1a59e4997c6d557adb059a.avif?t=1737715437\" width=800 height=532 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Followers of Jerry</h2>Join the ranks of the brainwashed followers of the Great Jerry the Parrot. Your task is simple: snatch up anyone in your path and bring them to our secret base, where they'll become one of us. No obstacles will hinder your devotion to Jerry.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2787750/extras/fd40df63bae2d6b574b70ca5f14b424d.avif?t=1737715437\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2787750/extras_big/fd40df63bae2d6b574b70ca5f14b424d.avif?t=1737715437 width=800 height=456 /></span><br><br><strong>Entities</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Partygoers</h2>Parties aren't meant to be enjoyed alone. Use your claws to gently encourage others to join our cause. A friendly pat is all it takes to motivate them to join the fun =). Partygoers will go into a chasing mode when they see a non enjoying wanderer! But they get tired prett quickly.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2787750/extras/72ec7089c9c2ba1d142ac2e424b766db.avif?t=1737715437\" width=758 height=628 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Smiler</h2>In the shadows, there's a smiling presence. Light sources won't work near it.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2787750/extras/5e83c03a53e61b428c0195513879e6d1.avif?t=1737715437\" width=726 height=594 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Skinstealer</h2>This humanoid creature seems harmless at first, but watch out when it gets hungry. Skinstealers can take on the appearance of their last victim, making them more dangerous than they appear.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2787750/extras/317d4c07ca171f2940509cf0546f5aee.avif?t=1737715437\" width=684 height=596 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Bacteria</h2>Beware of the immense, unidentified threat. Keep your distance to stay safe.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2787750/extras/50936b0531b44668a0acdec9d2ce8499.avif?t=1737715437\" width=736 height=574 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Backrooms: Liminal Conflict is a PvP backrooms game with different factions.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >M.E.G. Researcher</h2>Play as the M.E.G. Researcher class, trapped in the depths of the backrooms. Your objective: escape to the safety of an M.E.G. outpost. Along the way, you'll find aid from M.E.G. Mercenaries, ready to support you. But beware the Followers of Jerry, a sinister cult lurking in the shadows, intent on indoctrinating all wanderers in backrooms.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2787750/extras/0b03b8a46ed234c03fd6184e70bdea11.avif?t=1737715437\" width=598 height=444 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >M.E.G. Mercenary</h2>Take on the role of a M.E.G. Mercenary with a single directive: find and protect the researchers at all costs. Nothing will stand in your way as you eliminate any threats blocking your path.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2787750/extras/8102ac290c1a59e4997c6d557adb059a.avif?t=1737715437\" width=800 height=532 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Followers of Jerry</h2>Join the ranks of the brainwashed followers of the Great Jerry the Parrot. Your task is simple: snatch up anyone in your path and bring them to our secret base, where they'll become one of us. No obstacles will hinder your devotion to Jerry.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2787750/extras/fd40df63bae2d6b574b70ca5f14b424d.avif?t=1737715437\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2787750/extras_big/fd40df63bae2d6b574b70ca5f14b424d.avif?t=1737715437 width=800 height=456 /></span><br><br><strong>Entities</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Partygoers</h2>Parties aren't meant to be enjoyed alone. Use your claws to gently encourage others to join our cause. A friendly pat is all it takes to motivate them to join the fun =). Partygoers will go into a chasing mode when they see a non enjoying wanderer! But they get tired prett quickly.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2787750/extras/72ec7089c9c2ba1d142ac2e424b766db.avif?t=1737715437\" width=758 height=628 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Smiler</h2>In the shadows, there's a smiling presence. Light sources won't work near it.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2787750/extras/5e83c03a53e61b428c0195513879e6d1.avif?t=1737715437\" width=726 height=594 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Skinstealer</h2>This humanoid creature seems harmless at first, but watch out when it gets hungry. Skinstealers can take on the appearance of their last victim, making them more dangerous than they appear.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2787750/extras/317d4c07ca171f2940509cf0546f5aee.avif?t=1737715437\" width=684 height=596 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Bacteria</h2>Beware of the immense, unidentified threat. Keep your distance to stay safe.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2787750/extras/50936b0531b44668a0acdec9d2ce8499.avif?t=1737715437\" width=736 height=574 /></span>",
